U.S. Precious Metals Inc.


            
            U.S. Precious Metals, Inc. is an exploration stage company. The company engages in the acquisition, exploration and development of mineral properties. It focuses on gold, silver and copper mineral resource properties located in the state of Michoacán, Mexico. The company was founded on January 21, 1998 and is headquartered in Califon, NJ.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


